Package uk.ac.aber.dcs.cs12420.aberpizza.data

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Item
    Item interface which gives the 4 basic methods all Items in the Menu have
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Drinks
    Drinks class which inherits from SuperItem used to create drinks objects
    Main
    holds the main method of this Program
    Order
    Order class which holds an ArrayList of OrderItems and methods additional data like Customer name for the current order and the quantity of each object in the ArrayList of OrderItems
    OrderItem
    OrderItem class represents a link to an particular Item and the quantity for that Item
    Pizza
    Pizza class which inherits from SuperItem used to create Pizza objects
    Sides
    Sides class which inherits from SuperItem used to create Sides Objects
    SuperItem
    abstract SuperItem class which implements the Item interface holds all the common methods and fields which all 3 items in this program have
    Till
    Till class which holds an ArrayList of Orders holds method like save, load and getting the total for the day
